In [4]:
# unicode 範圍
# 英文 65~122
# 數字 48~57
def random_string(n):
    string = ''.join([chr(random.randint(48, 123)) for i in range(n)])
    return string

In [6]:
# 建立假資料
fake_data = []
for i in range(100):
    account = random_string(10)
    password = random_string(10)
    name = random_string(10)
    age = random.randint(16, 100)
    birth = datetime.date.today() - datetime.timedelta(days=365*age)
    dic = dict(zip(['account', 'password', 'name', 'age', 'birth'], [account, password, name, age, birth]))
    fake_data.append(dic)
